The,Hayo,API,allows,developers,to,build,apps,that,implement,virtual,remote,controls,for,connected,devices,in,a,home,The,API,senses,and,transmits,events,between,virtual,remote,controls,and,devices,making,it,easier,for,users,to,achieve,desired,actions,on,applications,by,simply,manipulating,a,virtual,remote,control,The,API,sends,requests,and,returns,responses,in,JSON,format